{"word":"φυσικός","slug":"φυσικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φυσικός</b></el> <el>(φῠσικός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φύσις'><el>φύσις</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>natural, native</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>διδακτός</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>of</i> or <i>in the order of nature, natural, physical</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>ἠθικός</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}